text: Daniel Turyna (born 26 February 1998) is a Czech footballer who plays for Sparta Prague as a forward. ==Career== ===FK Senica=== Turyna made his professional debut for FK Senica against ŠK Slovan Bratislava on 17 July 2016.FK Senica - ŠK Slovan Bratislava 0:1 (0:0) 17.07.2016, futbalnet.sk ==References== ==External links== * FK Senica official club profile * Eurofotbal profile * * Futbalnet Profile Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Czech footballers Category:Association football forwards Category:AC Sparta Prague players Category:FC Vysočina Jihlava players Category:SK Dynamo České Budějovice players Category:FK Senica players Category:Slovak Super Liga players Category:Expatriate footballers in Slovakia
